Auto set Anchor Overrides (Bad Lighting Fix)
Automatically sets anchor overrides for renderers that don't have them set already. This happens during avatar upload and fixes some common lighting issues ingame.

Name of a GameObject somewhere in your avatar's hierarchy to use as an anchor.\nIf not found the humanoid bone will be used.

This script will set Anchor Overrides for every mesh on your Avatar, preventing your body from experiencing flickering or uneven lighting in the game. We highly recommend you enable this automatic fix.
